3DExperience2016x implementation project – working as project consultant and key support as PLM architect. Involved in all phases of implementation project from server infrastructure analysis to server infrastructure analysis to business cases definition and functional validation of delivered solutions, making sure that delivered solutions are in line with business requirements. 

- Monitoring failure tests; 
- Guiding implementation solutions for system failures; 
- Leading improvements of business processes;
- Validation of EnoviaV6 integration with CatiaV6 and AutoCAD 2016, including PDF generation and title block.

Provide functional and technical support on existing productive system for EnoviaV6 2013x with CatiaV6 and AutoCAD 2012 integration.
